Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:12.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:18.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:24.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:30.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:47.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:01:01.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:06.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:13.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:24.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没有打倒这家伙的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也渐渐习惯这个身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  上面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第71话 一场混乱的死斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不了了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋…开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次换我将你大卸八块了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这浑蛋竟然这么跩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样根本没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜘蛛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的身体\N到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落原本就是\N由强盗鬼蜘蛛的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所维系的妖怪集合体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这个无双是\N从奈落的身体分离出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多妖怪也混杂着无双\N一起出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙和我们不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙对奈落而言\N是很特别的分身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为何无双能不断再生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是不死之身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早说过没用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不下去了\N难道就无计可施了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样连续的使用风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会累是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也承受了对方猛烈的攻势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你什么样子  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  用爆流破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用爆流破把他打的粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能用的话我早就用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆流破必须利用对手的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于只打肉搏战\N的无双派不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用风之伤  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再试试用风之伤将他打飞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我再能撑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样还是没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双的肉块
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以蜘蛛的周围为中心聚集着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那周围是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看  蜘蛛的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双以那个部分为中心\N汇集而重生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个地方在跳动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那的…可能是心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有值得一试的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别白费力气了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也差不多快喘不过气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤的轨道扩散成无数条
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一条
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实将那家伙的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击碎!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风刃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐那家伙用风刃\N影响了风之伤的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有命中无双的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这下子就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双的弱点是心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子他们也不打算隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上去  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  戈薇他们拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  还有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强盗鬼蜘蛛\N现在竟然再度复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双果然不只是奈落的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那家伙拥有鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不觉得很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么奈落要让无双…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落是想消除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思念桔梗的鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再杀了桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对奈落而言\N鬼蜘蛛应该是阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才将他放出体外的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是奈落却派出了\N神乐与最猛胜保护无双
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是用完就丢的分身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道奈落还是需要鬼蜘蛛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  犬夜叉那浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能除掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛…不  无双
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到会在\N这种情况下和你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…奈落吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是奈落吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相隔五十年的外界有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十年?你说五十年?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双  再度回到我的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也恨不得早一点\N舍弃你下流的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要放你走还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还太早?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经囚禁我五十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你而言只是一瞬间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十年前竟敢杀了桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你扭曲的欲望\N让妖怪们有机可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吞噬你身体的妖怪杀了桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是其中的一份子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是奈落  你应该很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望的只是得到桔梗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗的话  她已经复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同往昔的容貌般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也不算完全一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗还活着?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想得到她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里?桔梗在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法实现你这个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来吧  无双
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我一定要得到桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纠缠不休的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能不要干涉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双这家伙\N他想逃离奈落得到自由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想违逆奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落无法掌握这家伙的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是这家伙与我的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要回到我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事  奈落!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛…人类的心\N对你根本毫无用处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才用分身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将他放出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么又想要将他取回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为无双能打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但似乎是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要他回来  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是你将重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同无双一起放出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然好不容易\N舍弃的鬼蜘蛛的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能又取回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脑袋偶尔还挺灵光的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双随时能打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在这里要先除掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是认真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去追无双!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙和我同为奈落的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能任奈落随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他却打算逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么奈落在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是来取回无双的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因为将无双分开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而使自己变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:14:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太小看我奈落  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙将奈落…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…那家伙做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢蛋  你以为我会放过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手腕被吞进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我省去麻烦了  无双
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体竟然不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开  给我放开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到最后就是这种命运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我违背奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会变成这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  让我和桔梗见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这份执念  这股欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死心吧  无双
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的桔梗和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的身体是土与骨灰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的魂魄是过去的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无双被吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是\N需要鬼蜘蛛来维系我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的推理很正确  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维系?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我再问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再度将鬼蜘蛛的心\N吸进体内的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是半妖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的城\N结界出现了松散的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而让犬夜叉与钢牙等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗅觉灵敏的人闻到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那应该不是刻意造成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒这家伙到底想问出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要说\N我奈落也有变弱的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像所有的半妖一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候你的力量应该变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  何时会变弱\N是半妖的绝对秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他的半妖一样失去妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边躲避敌人一边发抖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听他这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子\N奈落真的没有从神乐那里听过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是朔日的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你的推论
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有无法行动的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我可以依照自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由人类与妖怪诞生的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本的构成就和我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不这么认为吗  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候奈落的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛身体整个解体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那段期间我一直在尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将强的部分组合得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃不必要的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让自己变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙能重制自己的身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在的确是半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能在自己\N选择的时刻只失去妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和只能偷偷摸摸躲避敌人\N的可怜半妖不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然叽哩呱啦废话一大堆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让你好好的安息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种结界算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤没效?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的结界到目前为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没有这么强才对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了  我会持续的变强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快避开  犬夜叉  是瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子奈落的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不全是唬人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要遇到朔日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管愿不愿意都会变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是奈落却不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是奈落能在\N重组身体的时候变强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会是很棘手的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这风真让人觉得不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不用你说也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  桔梗姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么  别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的结界弹回风之伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的确在变强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至  虽然同为半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朔日会失去妖力\N的犬夜叉不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落说他能选择那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说\N无法得知奈落何时会变弱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来想如果至少\N知道那家伙何时无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许能够打败他也不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛表情那么沉重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落也有无法行动的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我变得\N比那家伙更强不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N有时候你还蛮开朗的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是说他一直都很开朗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了  我的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行李?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丢在井边了  得快点去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星而已  有啥稀奇的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在现代看不到这么漂亮的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N我既是桔梗  又不是桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也没有理由抗拒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会如此被这份思念拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心…到底期望着什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:21.35,ED,,0,0,0,,究竟要流多少泪{\fad(500,0)}
